{"tid":146401,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今年18歲 已經諗好在人生計劃","createTime":"2017-03-07T05:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T04:25:30.000Z","uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96c02b5d69631475b1f1f574a584c291b9ab3fec","tid":146401,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"打算係今年返大陸搵個老婆，之後成家公屋綜援<br />\n再生返2-3個細路，到佢地18歲出黎做野我就退休<br />\n<br />\n即係40歲左右我就可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fda45b1ef26a77f45b28f7ca0ea5a1de6417e18","tid":146401,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"好想玩玩"},{"pid":"c3f835e971ee46a165d650302133631f1c3924c2","tid":146401,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想玩玩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4595864f4f657526df452a7cd771d034042df0","tid":146401,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打算係今年返大陸搵個老婆，之後成家公屋綜援<br />\n再生返2-3個細路，到佢地18歲出黎做野我就退休<br />\n<br />\n即係40歲左右我就可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n''返大陸''?<br />\n用個返字, 即係你都係大陸黎<br />\n走喇! 返去自己既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1315044577d92c2aa647057ad102f03dc86f78a0","tid":146401,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"41 歲 RIP    ,  因為你畀個大陸婆毒死左"},{"pid":"c88f5233aa94ab0cf68847799067acc49855ff3d","tid":146401,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打算係今年返大陸搵個老婆，之後成家公屋綜援<br />\n再生返2-3個細路，到佢地18歲出黎做野我就退休<br />\n<br />\n即係40歲左右我就可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每隔1-2年生一個，<br />\n以照顧孩子為由拒絕工作，<br />\n生夠7個，申請公屋大單位。<br />\n<br />\n有人係咁"},{"pid":"acbb47bd89274f04bce148ac0d625a4bea416692","tid":146401,"uid":10571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"d12a6ee0d570e913be964e7d8da3608a792ac6eb","tid":146401,"uid":34511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。</blockquote><br />\n佢宜家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eee93f195348d757e7d2bd746e73bc5219a073","tid":146401,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打算係今年返大陸搵個老婆，之後成家公屋綜援<br />\n再生返2-3個細路，到佢地18歲出黎做野我就退休<br />\n<br />\n即係40歲左右我就可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n''返大陸''?<br />\n用個返字, 即係你都係大陸黎<br />\n走喇! 返去自己既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祖籍國內"},{"pid":"ab7ebe3dfd06f6b414b0c463fc2d0b999d03c5c8","tid":146401,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打算係今年返大陸搵個老婆，之後成家公屋綜援<br />\n再生返2-3個細路，到佢地18歲出黎做野我就退休<br />\n<br />\n即係40歲左右我就可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每隔1-2年生一個，<br />\n以照顧孩子為由拒絕工作，<br />\n生夠7個，申請公屋大單位。<br />\n<br />\n有人係咁</blockquote><br />\n到時有4房公屋，拎緊幾萬綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f7a39acf6840d5b61226fa3b214ec67a530dca","tid":146401,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想玩玩</blockquote><br />\n未入已經諗到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1cd134a2804eccfc6561381649326b1de568bc","tid":146401,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b56769422ebb85efd05b9fa767c50a35781e994","tid":146401,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"咁至係人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}